{"tid":2434948,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登提名鷹派學者吳修銘加入白宮經濟委員會 被指欲向科技巨頭開刀","createTime":"2021-03-06T01:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T02:08:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"af9839a4273f72098e39c4265c1299952917d547","tid":2434948,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕《紐約時報》今天報導，美國總統拜登週五（6）將提名鷹派學者、也是現任哥倫比亞大學法學院教授吳修銘（Tim Wu）擔任技術及競爭擔任科技及市場競爭政策的總統特別助理，外界預期，因吳修銘是知名的科技巨頭鷹派人士，拜登邀請其加入白宮經濟委員會（NEC），被解讀為可能對亞馬遜、蘋果、Facebook及谷歌等科技巨頭開刀。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述白宮官員稱，拜登將在周五提名哥倫比亞大學法學教授吳修銘（Tim Wu）加入國家經濟委員會，並擔任科技和市場競爭政策的總統特別助理。現年48歲的吳修銘受到民主黨人士和反壟斷組織的廣泛支持，此舉透露拜登政府計劃對亞馬遜、蘋果、Facebook和Google等公司的規模和影響力出手，包括與國會合作制定相關法律，以加強反壟斷法。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3457797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457797&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=3446c39c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457797&h=e3c96df4\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3457797</a>"},{"pid":"fd572e678e4c7db8b45f6b50b7746b9117a9f8c6","tid":2434948,"uid":36739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:02:53.000Z","msg":"對美鷹派？"},{"pid":"bba3507609b4f565d5bc2b5106f529e6e607e85a","tid":2434948,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:54:25.000Z","msg":"等睇google Facebook Amazon去上証上市<br />\nChina joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d147f7cc7d3fd244eedc64d9b065cbf1bcc0b9fb","tid":2434948,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd572e678e4c7db8b45f6b50b7746b9117a9f8c6","tid":2434948,"uid":36739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:02:53.000Z","msg":"對美鷹派？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"